SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT DISTINCT a.Navigation_ID, a.Navigation_Name, a.Nav_URL, a.Sort_Order FROM Navigations AS a INNER JOIN subscription_navigations AS b ON a.Navigation_ID = b.Navigation_Id INNER JOIN Entity_Subscription AS c ON b.Subscription_Type_Id = c.Subscription_Type_ID WHERE (c.Entity_ID = :1 ) AND (c.End_Date > GETDATE()) UNION SELECT d.Navigation_ID, d.Navigation_Name, d.Nav_URL, d.Sort_Order FROM Navigations AS d, subscription_navigations e WHERE d.Navigation_ID = e.Navigation_Id AND e.Subscription_Type_ID = 0 ORDER BY a.Sort_Order
